text: Ik () is a rural locality (a village) in Tarkazinsky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 31 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 53 km from Yermekeyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Ik, Yermekeyevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
